# Tarball uploaded to ACR for `az acr build` / `docker build`.
# Keep this minimal: only the source the Dockerfile actually COPYs.

**/node_modules
**/dist
**/out
**/.git
**/.vscode
**/.azure
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/coverage
**/*.log
**/*.vsix
**/.DS_Store

# Test, doc, and release artefacts not needed in the image.
**/__tests__
**/__snapshots__
**/*.test.ts
**/*.test.js
**/test-results
**/releases
**/presentations
**/Research
**/change-requests
**/whitepapers
**/docs/templates

# We do need docs/knowledge and docs/bestpractices (Dockerfile copies docs/).
!docs/knowledge
!docs/knowledge/**
!docs/bestpractices
!docs/bestpractices/**
!packages/core
!packages/core/**
!packages/mcp-server
!packages/mcp-server/**

# But re-exclude the heavy stuff inside those packages.
packages/*/node_modules
packages/*/dist
packages/*/out
packages/*/coverage
packages/extension
packages/core/__tests__
packages/mcp-server/__tests__
